description:
Genre: Arcade / 3D / 3rd Person / Adventure / For Kids


Interface: English (ENG)

Multiplayer: Yes

Unbelievable Adventures of prehistoric Arctic friends!

After drying the earth split into many continents (with the help of one excessively curious krysobelka), began the most exciting adventure of the greatest heroes of the prehistoric world. And once it has led them to one of the most mysterious places of the Earth - the Arctic!

Powerful and moody mammoth, wildly talkative sloth, a proud and loyal saber-toothed tiger, the same krysobelka possessed with a passion for acorns, and other favorite characters are waiting for you in the game based on the animated film &quot;Ice Age 4: Continental Drift.&quot; Join the heroes of the Ice Age in this stunning multiplatform shooter. 


-System: Microsoft Windows XP / Vista / Seven; 
-Processor: Intel Core 2 Duo 2.4 Ghz; 
-Memory: 1 Gb; 
-Video Card: 256 Mb, Shader Model 3.0, c support for DirectX 9.0c; 
-Sound Card: Sound device compatible with DirectX 9.0; 
-Hard disk: 2 GB;

Install: Install in folder of your choice.

Before start installing, disable your Anti-virus.

Game is tested and works perfect.




